b.2004.12.018 }}</ref>\n| [[Keratin]] [[intermediate filament]] proteins\n|-\n| Corneal lactoferrin [[amyloidosis]]\n| [[Lactoferrin]]<ref name=\"Sipe 2016\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sipe JD, Benson MD, Buxbaum JN, Ikeda SI, Merlini G, Saraiva MJ, Westermark P | title = Amyloid fibril proteins and amyloidosis: chemical identification and clinical classification International Society of Amyloidosis 2016 Nomenclature Guidelines | journal = Amyloid | volume = 23 | issue = 4 | pages = 209\u2013213 | date = December 2016 | pmid = 27884064 | doi = 10.1080/13506129.2016.1257986 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Pulmonary alveolar proteinosis]]\n| [[Surfactant protein C]] (SP-C)<ref name=\"Sipe 2016\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sipe JD, Benson MD, Buxbaum JN, Ikeda SI, Merlini G, Saraiva MJ, Westermark P | title = Amyloid fibril proteins and amyloidosis: chemical identification and clinical classification International Society of Amyloidosis 2016 Nomenclature Guidelines | journal = Amyloid | volume = 23 | issue = 4 | pages = 209\u2013213 | date = December 2016 | pmid = 27884064 | doi = 10.1080/13506129.2016.1257986 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Calcifying epithelial odontogenic tumor|Odontogenic (Pindborg) tumor amyloid]]\n| [[ODAM (gene)|Odontogenic ameloblast-associated protein]]<ref name=\"Sipe 2016\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sipe JD, Benson MD, Buxbaum JN, Ikeda SI, Merlini G, Saraiva MJ, Westermark P | title = Amyloid fibril proteins and amyloidosis: chemical identification and clinical classification International Society of Amyloidosis 2016 Nomenclature Guidelines | journal = Amyloid | volume = 23 | issue = 4 | pages = 209\u2013213 | date = December 2016 | pmid = 27884064 | doi = 10.1080/13506129.2016.1257986 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Seminal vesicle]] amyloid\n| [[Semenogelin I]]<ref name=\"Sipe 2016\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sipe JD, Benson MD, Buxbaum JN, Ikeda SI, Merlini G, Saraiva MJ, Westermark P | title = Amyloid fibril proteins and amyloidosis: chemical identification and clinical c