iplex Offers The Asterisk War Season 1 on English-Dubbed Blu-ray | work = Anime News Network | date=2016-06-04 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[One-Punch Man]]'' || [[List of One-Punch Man characters#Saitama|Saitama]] || Also OVAs || <ref>{{cite web|title=Max Mittleman Stars in One-Punch Man English Dub|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-07-01/max-mittleman-stars-in-one-punch-man-english-dub/.103848|website=Anime News Network|accessdate=1 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2017 || ''[[Berserk (2016 TV series)|Berserk]]'' || Serpico || 25 episodes || <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MaxMittelman/status/843002758080868352|title=Cool announcement from earlier today is that I'm Serpico in the upcoming Berserk release!|last=Mittelman|first=Max|date=2017-03-18|website=@MaxMittelman|access-date=2017-06-05}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Occultic;Nine]]'' || Shun Moritsuka || || <ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2017-05-22/aniplex-of-america-announces-paranormal-anime-occultic-nine-for-blu-ray-release-and-english-dub/.116435 | title = Aniplex of America Announces Paranormal Anime Occultic;nine for Blu-ray Release and English Dub | work = Anime News Network | date=May 22, 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Mobile Suit Gundam SEED]]'' || [[Kira Yamato]] || 30 episodes; NYAV Post dub || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-08-11/sunrise-to-release-gundam-seed-gundam-seed-destiny-with-new-english-dub/.120036|title=Sunrise to Release Gundam SEED, Destiny with New English Dub|publisher=Anime News Network|date=August 11, 2017|accessdate=August 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny]]'' || [[Kira Yamato]] || 36 episodes || \n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2018 || ''[[Bungo Stray Dogs]]'' || Atsushi Nakajima ||  || \n|-\n| ''[[Hunter \u00d7 Hunter]]'' || [[List of Hunter \u00d7 Hunter characters#Meruem|Meruem]] || 2 episodes || <ref>{{cite episode | at=Closing credits | title= The Strong \u00d7 And \u00d7 The Weak | publis